WEBVTT

00:00:12.712 --> 00:00:14.114
We're home.

00:00:14.180 --> 00:00:15.949
-Welcome back.
-We're back.

00:00:16.016 --> 00:00:17.851
-Hey, guys.
-It was fun.

00:00:17.917 --> 00:00:19.419
-You had fun?
-Yeah.

00:00:19.486 --> 00:00:21.154
Yes, we had fun.

00:00:23.056 --> 00:00:23.923
They're back.

00:00:24.624 --> 00:00:25.725
Where are they?

00:00:27.193 --> 00:00:28.261
There they are.

00:00:32.098 --> 00:00:34.134
-Welcome back!
-Yoo-hoo!

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:35.535
-Welcome back.
-We're back.

00:00:35.602 --> 00:00:36.636
We're home.

00:00:36.703 --> 00:00:37.937
Everyone is here.

00:00:38.538 --> 00:00:39.906
Yeah, we're all here.

00:00:39.973 --> 00:00:40.807
Welcome back.

00:00:40.874 --> 00:00:43.009
Any developments?

00:00:43.076 --> 00:00:44.411
Too many.

00:00:44.477 --> 00:00:45.311
Really?

00:00:46.246 --> 00:00:47.080
There were.

00:00:49.149 --> 00:00:51.251
How about you? Any developments?

00:00:51.317 --> 00:00:52.485
Yeah.

00:00:52.552 --> 00:00:54.187
What kind?

00:00:54.954 --> 00:00:55.955
We slept together.

00:00:56.489 --> 00:00:58.191
-What?
-We slept together.

00:00:58.258 --> 00:00:59.292
You mean you had sex?

00:00:59.359 --> 00:01:00.560
Yes.

00:01:00.627 --> 00:01:02.128
What? Really?

00:01:04.664 --> 00:01:05.698
It's a lie.

00:01:05.765 --> 00:01:07.534
-A lie?
-Lying from the get-go.

00:01:09.202 --> 00:01:11.171
No way they'd tell us
if they really did it.

00:01:11.237 --> 00:01:12.105
Yeah?

00:01:12.639 --> 00:01:13.740
Did you guys kiss?

00:01:16.476 --> 00:01:17.510
You did.

00:01:26.119 --> 00:01:28.254
-I see the afterglow.
-Oh, an afterglow.

00:01:28.321 --> 00:01:30.090
The kiss must've been good.

00:01:30.623 --> 00:01:32.759
-The kiss.
-The afterglow from a kiss.

00:01:32.826 --> 00:01:35.195
-The afterglow from the kiss is…
-So long!

00:01:35.261 --> 00:01:36.830
It's lingering.

00:01:38.865 --> 00:01:42.969
-That was a great kiss.
-Shun is so transparent.

00:01:43.036 --> 00:01:46.406
Dai must be simultaneously thinking,
"Please stop" and "You're too cute."

00:01:49.742 --> 00:01:51.311
I have a lot to ask you.

00:01:51.377 --> 00:01:52.879
Sure, ask me anything.

00:01:53.446 --> 00:01:56.783
When your name was called with Ryota's,

00:01:56.850 --> 00:01:58.151
you looked happy.

00:01:58.218 --> 00:01:59.285
Did I?

00:01:59.352 --> 00:02:04.390
But it wasn't
an obviously happy face like Dai's.

00:02:07.393 --> 00:02:10.063
I've known for a while now

00:02:10.130 --> 00:02:14.734
that Ryota had feelings for Kazuto.

00:02:15.535 --> 00:02:19.739
I was happy about the date itself,
but I had mixed feelings.

00:02:20.874 --> 00:02:21.941
I see.

00:02:22.008 --> 00:02:23.276
Yeah.

00:02:23.343 --> 00:02:25.745
-We all came back this morning, right?
-Yeah.

00:02:26.312 --> 00:02:29.682
I think Ryota looked a little sad.

00:02:30.483 --> 00:02:34.454
When Kazuto and Alan came back,

00:02:35.088 --> 00:02:39.492
I sensed it bothered him a bit.

00:02:41.027 --> 00:02:44.164
So what are you going to do now?

00:02:44.230 --> 00:02:48.668
Telling him how I feel right now

00:02:49.702 --> 00:02:53.373
would be counterproductive, I think.

00:02:53.439 --> 00:02:54.507
At this point.

00:02:55.808 --> 00:02:58.811
I need to have emotional space

00:02:59.412 --> 00:03:01.247
before I tell him my feelings.

00:03:01.314 --> 00:03:02.916
That would be for the best.

00:03:03.616 --> 00:03:05.652
This is something Alan said.

00:03:05.718 --> 00:03:08.655
"Ask yourself
if it'll make you happy or not

00:03:08.721 --> 00:03:10.823
when you make a choice."

00:03:10.890 --> 00:03:14.494
He said that's what he keeps in mind.

00:03:14.561 --> 00:03:18.565
I completely agree with that.

00:03:18.631 --> 00:03:22.035
Will it make me happy or not?

00:03:22.101 --> 00:03:25.872
The question should be simple,
and I just need to take action.

00:03:26.472 --> 00:03:30.610
But even if I tell Ryota my feelings,

00:03:30.677 --> 00:03:33.079
I don't think I'll be happy.

00:03:34.214 --> 00:03:35.148
I see.

00:03:35.949 --> 00:03:38.885
I'm going to think it over tonight.

00:03:39.519 --> 00:03:41.287
But don't overthink it.

00:03:41.354 --> 00:03:42.689
Yeah, you're right.

00:03:43.957 --> 00:03:46.059
Are you doing okay?

00:03:46.626 --> 00:03:50.163
Well, the other day, I asked everyone
about their coming out experiences.

00:03:50.230 --> 00:03:51.431
Right.

00:03:52.365 --> 00:03:54.334
You guys gave me courage.

00:03:54.834 --> 00:03:55.668
But…

00:03:58.471 --> 00:04:00.373
but I'm still scared.

00:04:01.341 --> 00:04:03.076
I don't know what to do.

00:04:03.142 --> 00:04:05.511
I'm definitely going to tell them.

00:04:06.012 --> 00:04:07.680
But how should I tell them?

00:04:08.414 --> 00:04:12.218
They could react in a few different ways.

00:04:12.885 --> 00:04:14.254
But it's twice the shock.

00:04:15.655 --> 00:04:18.191
Your daughter is… No, not daughter.

00:04:18.958 --> 00:04:23.363
Your son is gay.

00:04:23.429 --> 00:04:28.735
In addition, the world will know about it.

00:04:29.769 --> 00:04:33.072
So I'm concerned about what they'll think.

00:04:34.474 --> 00:04:38.578
But it could be a good opportunity.

00:04:39.646 --> 00:04:44.951
I mean, If you hadn't done the show,
when would you have told them?

00:04:45.018 --> 00:04:50.923
I didn't have a road map or specific time
I was going to tell them.

00:04:52.058 --> 00:04:53.693
-But you wanted to tell them.
-Yeah.

00:04:54.460 --> 00:04:55.928
Then it's a good opportunity.

00:04:57.230 --> 00:04:59.532
-You're right.
-You're not doing anything wrong.

00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:02.001
During my stay here,

00:05:02.068 --> 00:05:07.373
I feel like I've made real connections,
not just friends who meet up for drinks.

00:05:07.974 --> 00:05:09.475
I feel supported.

00:05:10.209 --> 00:05:14.113
I think I'll be able to tell them
without overthinking it.

00:05:14.614 --> 00:05:16.949
That's good. We both won't overthink it.

00:05:17.016 --> 00:05:19.585
-Right.
-Don't worry, you can do it.

00:05:24.223 --> 00:05:27.593
Taeheon hasn't experienced romance here,

00:05:27.660 --> 00:05:30.129
but he still has his own story going on.

00:05:30.196 --> 00:05:33.132
-That's true.
-I think that's really beautiful.

00:05:33.199 --> 00:05:35.968
Gensei, too, is not certain

00:05:36.035 --> 00:05:39.639
if telling Ryota his feelings
would make him happy or not.

00:05:39.706 --> 00:05:40.540
True.

00:05:40.606 --> 00:05:44.277
Maybe he feels like troubling Ryota
wouldn't make him happy.

00:05:44.344 --> 00:05:45.778
-Right.
-Yeah.

00:07:03.189 --> 00:07:04.690
-Eating separately?
-What?

00:07:04.757 --> 00:07:05.992
-Why?
-Wait a minute.

00:07:13.699 --> 00:07:15.368
Good morning, Taeheon.

00:07:16.936 --> 00:07:21.240
I don't know what Shun is unhappy about.

00:07:22.575 --> 00:07:23.476
Well,

00:07:24.477 --> 00:07:29.615
maybe he didn't like something I did.

00:07:29.682 --> 00:07:30.616
You know,

00:07:31.617 --> 00:07:35.822
perhaps something negative happened,

00:07:35.888 --> 00:07:37.557
and there's a reaction incoming.

00:07:39.158 --> 00:07:40.460
What happened?

00:07:40.526 --> 00:07:42.762
-Overnight? No way.
-That's too quick.

00:07:44.831 --> 00:07:45.998
There's the ding.

00:07:46.566 --> 00:07:47.667
"Good morning."

00:07:47.733 --> 00:07:49.902
-Good morning.
-Good morning.

00:07:49.969 --> 00:07:51.671
"Today's shift will be announced."

00:07:51.737 --> 00:07:54.006
-Here it comes.
-Please go ahead.

00:07:55.908 --> 00:07:57.343
"Today,

00:07:58.978 --> 00:08:01.080
Gensei will take the shift."

00:08:03.783 --> 00:08:07.920
"Gensei, please choose one person
you would like to work with."

00:08:07.987 --> 00:08:09.055
-What?
-One person?

00:08:09.589 --> 00:08:11.457
Gen gets to choose.

00:08:12.024 --> 00:08:14.393
Gen's feelings will be made clear.

00:08:36.482 --> 00:08:37.750
Please work with me.

00:08:37.817 --> 00:08:38.651
Me?

00:08:39.852 --> 00:08:41.087
Is it okay?

00:08:41.153 --> 00:08:42.021
I'd love to.

00:08:46.759 --> 00:08:47.727
Have fun.

00:08:49.195 --> 00:08:51.931
Can I put some makeup on you?
You're looking tired today.

00:08:53.599 --> 00:08:55.201
-You really look tired.
-Please.

