-That's rude.
-He's got dark circles.

00:09:02.808 --> 00:09:05.244
Let's avoid covering the freckles.

00:09:05.311 --> 00:09:06.612
Yeah, please.

00:09:06.679 --> 00:09:08.681
-That's part of my charm.
-Yeah.

00:09:28.334 --> 00:09:29.902
-Great!
-He looks amazing.

00:09:29.969 --> 00:09:31.504
You could grow out the back.

00:09:32.238 --> 00:09:33.306
-Starting now?
-Yeah.

00:09:33.940 --> 00:09:36.442
It's nice to do hair and makeup
for someone you love.

00:09:36.509 --> 00:09:39.645
When doing makeup,
his serious face is up close to you.

00:09:39.712 --> 00:09:41.380
Right. Your heart would pound.

00:09:55.528 --> 00:09:56.629
-Okay.
-All right.

00:09:57.530 --> 00:09:59.565
Did you practice drawing?

00:09:59.632 --> 00:10:00.967
No, I didn't.

00:10:13.512 --> 00:10:17.316
You could work as a real barista anywhere.

00:10:17.883 --> 00:10:20.586
Your movement is graceful and efficient.

00:10:20.653 --> 00:10:23.189
Thank you. I'm flattered.

00:10:23.689 --> 00:10:25.591
Here's the guava juice.

00:10:25.658 --> 00:10:28.961
-Feel free to use the straws.
-Thank you.

00:10:29.028 --> 00:10:30.529
Thank you very much.

00:10:33.466 --> 00:10:34.333
All right!

00:10:36.202 --> 00:10:37.203
1,900 yen.

00:10:38.204 --> 00:10:41.974
-We surpassed the first day.
-We did.

00:10:42.608 --> 00:10:44.143
Let's do it.

00:10:44.210 --> 00:10:45.177
A fond memory.

00:10:47.780 --> 00:10:50.683
-The handwriting incident.
-Right, the misunderstanding.

00:10:59.225 --> 00:11:01.460
Let's make a list
of what we're doing today.

00:11:01.527 --> 00:11:04.597
-Gym and sunbathing.
-And the pool, right?

00:11:05.097 --> 00:11:06.065
May I be by myself?

00:11:06.132 --> 00:11:07.466
-What?
-Why?

00:11:08.034 --> 00:11:09.535
It's okay, but what happened?

00:11:09.602 --> 00:11:12.071
I can't enjoy myself if we're together.

00:11:14.206 --> 00:11:16.175
I need a little space.

00:11:16.742 --> 00:11:17.777
From us?

00:11:19.578 --> 00:11:20.579
From that person.

00:11:22.481 --> 00:11:23.349
From Dai?

00:11:23.416 --> 00:11:24.250
Yeah.

00:11:24.784 --> 00:11:26.886
Dai, you must be wondering why.

00:11:28.187 --> 00:11:31.157
If you have something to say,
you need to talk about it.

00:11:31.223 --> 00:11:32.958
Feelings can change.

00:11:36.829 --> 00:11:37.863
It's a hassle.

00:11:41.233 --> 00:11:43.369
-What about you, Dai? Anything?
-No.

00:11:43.436 --> 00:11:44.403
-Nothing?
-No.

00:11:49.675 --> 00:11:51.877
Dai may have had enough…

00:11:51.944 --> 00:11:53.846
It's exhausting.

00:11:53.913 --> 00:11:55.347
He keeps pouring his love…

00:11:55.414 --> 00:11:57.750
-But it's not accumulating.
-That's right.

00:11:57.817 --> 00:12:00.086
What happened?

00:12:04.857 --> 00:12:07.460
There's one thing that comes to mind.

00:12:08.627 --> 00:12:10.162
Well, yesterday,

00:12:10.663 --> 00:12:13.299
before I took a bath,

00:12:14.300 --> 00:12:17.536
Shun said, "You can wear this T-shirt.
I just wore it for a sec."

00:12:18.270 --> 00:12:21.006
I said, "I'm good. I have a new one."

00:12:21.073 --> 00:12:23.109
But he insisted that it was clean.

00:12:23.175 --> 00:12:25.911
So I just said "okay" and took it.

00:12:26.479 --> 00:12:30.683
But I just wore what I was going to wear.

00:12:31.517 --> 00:12:36.055
I put on my own shirt
and went upstairs for a face mask,

00:12:36.122 --> 00:12:37.957
and Shun said, "You're not wearing it."

00:12:38.023 --> 00:12:40.092
-That's definitely it.
-Yeah.

00:12:42.128 --> 00:12:43.395
Everyone already knows.

00:12:43.462 --> 00:12:45.397
-Yeah.
-How Shun thinks.

00:12:45.965 --> 00:12:50.970
"I'm sorry for not wearing your T-shirt"?
Do I even need to apologize for that?

00:12:51.036 --> 00:12:52.772
You know what…

00:12:52.838 --> 00:12:57.042
what you're seeing
and feeling on your end.

00:12:57.676 --> 00:12:59.512
Why don't you just be honest with him?

00:12:59.578 --> 00:13:02.214
It's not that I don't want to tell him.

00:13:02.281 --> 00:13:07.119
It feels wrong that I have to initiate.

00:13:10.189 --> 00:13:11.123
Let's chat.

00:13:11.190 --> 00:13:12.391
-Sure. Are you sure?
-Yeah.

00:13:12.458 --> 00:13:13.959
I'm a bit worried.

00:13:14.026 --> 00:13:14.994
About what?

00:13:15.060 --> 00:13:16.295
-About you.
-Me?

00:13:16.362 --> 00:13:17.196
Yeah.

00:13:17.263 --> 00:13:20.866
It's painful to watch you.

00:13:20.933 --> 00:13:21.867
For real?

00:13:21.934 --> 00:13:23.903
You hold yourself back for him.

00:13:23.969 --> 00:13:26.172
He tosses your feelings around.

00:13:27.673 --> 00:13:30.442
I'm thinking it's too painful for you.

00:13:31.544 --> 00:13:35.181
I want to keep trying…
even if it wears me down.

00:13:37.550 --> 00:13:40.019
I don't know which of us
will wear down first.

00:13:42.588 --> 00:13:47.726
You were so supportive of me,
so I wanted to support you.

00:13:47.793 --> 00:13:49.295
Oh, you're sweet.

00:13:49.895 --> 00:13:52.765
You know, if there's something

00:13:52.832 --> 00:13:55.100
that's making you react that strongly,

00:13:55.634 --> 00:14:02.474
it means you must be feeling something
in terms of romance, right?

00:14:02.541 --> 00:14:04.109
That's true. But I…

00:14:04.176 --> 00:14:07.947
That's what I thought.
I'll support you as much as I can.

00:14:08.013 --> 00:14:08.848
Yeah.

00:14:12.551 --> 00:14:13.519
Does he like Dai?

00:14:13.586 --> 00:14:16.689
That face means he likes Dai, right?

00:14:16.755 --> 00:14:21.327
But it could be that he can't let go
of his feelings for Kazuto, right?

00:14:21.393 --> 00:14:23.929
Yes, that's also possible
from his expression.

00:14:23.996 --> 00:14:27.333
-What does his expression mean?
-I know.

00:14:27.399 --> 00:14:28.601
Not again, Shun…

00:14:28.667 --> 00:14:30.736
Shun and Dai will do this forever.

00:14:30.803 --> 00:14:33.005
Forever. It's a cycle.

00:14:33.072 --> 00:14:36.208
Dai says he wants to keep trying
even if it wears him down.

00:14:36.275 --> 00:14:37.710
That's impressive.

00:14:37.776 --> 00:14:39.979
Not many people could say that.

00:14:40.045 --> 00:14:42.781
-I've never heard anyone say that before.
-Incredible.

00:14:42.848 --> 00:14:44.984
He's never felt this way before.

00:14:45.050 --> 00:14:46.285
-Right.
-That's true.

00:14:46.352 --> 00:14:48.153
It's precious to him.

00:14:50.489 --> 00:14:51.423
What a waste.

00:14:52.124 --> 00:14:53.392
Yeah, I know.

00:14:55.027 --> 00:14:56.061
It's fine though.

00:14:57.963 --> 00:14:59.965
Are you going to talk to him?

00:15:01.133 --> 00:15:03.469
Yeah, I'll find a good time for it.

00:15:05.337 --> 00:15:06.338
I'll talk to him.

00:15:07.406 --> 00:15:09.041
Tell us if you need anything.

00:15:25.758 --> 00:15:27.126
-Is it good?
-Yeah.

00:15:29.094 --> 00:15:30.429
It's time for a nap.

00:15:30.496 --> 00:15:31.330
I see.

00:15:32.765 --> 00:15:33.866
What's going on?

00:15:34.800 --> 00:15:35.701
What's up?

00:15:36.468 --> 00:15:38.604
What caused this?

00:15:39.638 --> 00:15:41.573
-I don't want to tell you.
-Why?

00:15:42.308 --> 00:15:43.509
It's minor.

00:15:44.677 --> 00:15:48.647
It's big for me,
but others would say, "What the heck?"

00:15:48.714 --> 00:15:49.782
I don't wanna say.

00:15:51.383 --> 00:15:53.552
What? I really don't understand.

00:15:54.353 --> 00:15:59.058
What is Ikuo thinking?
Why is he talking to Shun?

00:15:59.558 --> 00:16:01.927
We don't know the answer to that.

00:16:02.461 --> 00:16:06.298
I'm sure he wants to do something
for you guys.

00:16:06.799 --> 00:16:10.502
But it's probably
an unnecessary interference in your eyes.

00:16:10.569 --> 00:16:14.106
I'm sure he's not trying to be malicious.

00:16:14.173 --> 00:16:16.308
Yeah, that's true.

00:16:16.375 --> 00:16:19.278
I talk a lot,

00:16:20.112 --> 00:16:23.983
but I'm bad at articulating
my thoughts to someone.

00:16:24.049 --> 00:16:28.587
The frustration of being unable
to find the words makes me emotional.

00:16:28.654 --> 00:16:30.022
-Yeah.
-We get it.

00:16:30.089 --> 00:16:33.425
-I'm afraid of that, so I'm intentionally…
-You don't want to hurt him.

00:16:33.492 --> 00:16:38.731
That's why I try to
temporarily distance myself.

00:16:39.865 --> 00:16:41.066
That's where I'm at now.

00:16:41.600 --> 00:16:46.705
You both know that your feelings mesh.

00:16:46.772 --> 00:16:50.309
But if you don't put it into words
while we're living together,

00:16:50.376 --> 00:16:52.611
it worries everyone else too.

00:16:53.178 --> 00:16:56.248
I think you two should talk about it,

00:16:56.315 --> 00:16:59.118
but if that's hard,
you could do it in our presence too.

00:17:01.353 --> 00:17:02.421
Then I'll do that.

00:17:02.488 --> 00:17:03.655
-You want us there?
-Yeah.

00:17:04.223 --> 00:17:08.427
I want to hear everyone's opinion too.

00:17:08.494 --> 00:17:09.728
Should I call them?

00:17:09.795 --> 00:17:10.896
Are you okay?

00:17:10.963 --> 00:17:12.831
You're ready? I'll go get them.

00:17:13.465 --> 00:17:14.333
Okay.

00:17:24.276 --> 00:17:25.210
Hey, guys.

00:17:26.245 --> 00:17:29.081
Well, after Shun and I discussed this,

00:17:30.749 --> 00:17:31.650
well,

00:17:32.985 --> 00:17:39.658
we agreed he wants to convey his feelings
with everyone present.

00:17:39.725 --> 00:17:42.261
Can we have a moment of your time?

00:17:43.028 --> 00:17:45.330
Hey, why did you do that? Seriously.

00:17:49.968 --> 00:17:53.906
-What made you think it's a good idea?
-I'm not trying to force you.

00:17:53.972 --> 00:17:56.942
But everyone here is tiptoeing around you.

