00:38:05.449 --> 00:38:06.917
Thank you.

00:38:08.686 --> 00:38:11.656
Seriously, I was panicked.
Thank you, Mr. Ikuo, for keeping calm.

00:38:11.722 --> 00:38:12.890
No problem at all.

00:38:12.957 --> 00:38:14.959
We're training to make coffee.

00:38:15.026 --> 00:38:17.395
-We can have some now?
-Yes, please!

00:38:17.461 --> 00:38:19.030
I'm going to have one, then.

00:38:20.131 --> 00:38:21.565
Good job, Mr. Ikuo.

00:38:22.366 --> 00:38:24.235
Here, before these get cold.

00:38:24.302 --> 00:38:26.270
Here are two small hot lattes.

00:38:26.837 --> 00:38:29.974
Here are small hot lattes. Two.

00:38:30.041 --> 00:38:32.376
We'll now make the iced and the hot.

00:38:32.443 --> 00:38:33.411
-Yes.
-Okay.

00:38:34.445 --> 00:38:36.347
-Can you grab a medium lid?
-Okay.

00:38:36.414 --> 00:38:38.015
Sorry, I know you're busy. Thanks.

00:38:38.082 --> 00:38:40.084
We're both busy.

00:38:41.018 --> 00:38:42.286
Let's support each other.

00:38:42.353 --> 00:38:43.454
You're amazing.

00:38:43.521 --> 00:38:46.724
We're sorry for the chaos.
Thank you for the wait.

00:38:46.791 --> 00:38:49.427
-Thank you.
-Thank you very much. Take care.

00:38:51.796 --> 00:38:53.531
-Can you see them?
-Yeah!

00:38:53.597 --> 00:38:54.932
-No way.
-By the window.

00:38:54.999 --> 00:38:56.634
-Where?
-By the window.

00:38:57.201 --> 00:38:58.402
Second from the top.

00:38:59.170 --> 00:39:00.404
Toward the front.

00:39:04.342 --> 00:39:05.476
I'm glad!

00:39:06.711 --> 00:39:07.878
That was wonderful.

00:39:08.479 --> 00:39:10.214
-Yeah!
-So amazing.

00:39:17.455 --> 00:39:19.490
I wanna know why you chose me.

00:39:21.025 --> 00:39:22.026
It's simple.

00:39:23.794 --> 00:39:25.363
There's something I wanted to say.

00:39:25.429 --> 00:39:27.031
About yesterday.

00:39:28.199 --> 00:39:30.801
Hey, why did you do that? Seriously.

00:39:32.002 --> 00:39:36.907
I never imagined
my actions would cause so much trouble.

00:39:36.974 --> 00:39:37.808
Yeah.

00:39:38.442 --> 00:39:41.679
I wanted to say I'm sorry.

00:39:41.746 --> 00:39:43.614
Thank you for your thoughtfulness.

00:39:45.149 --> 00:39:48.986
-But there's another personal reason.
-What is it?

00:39:49.653 --> 00:39:54.992
I think everyone thinks
I have feelings for Kazuto.

00:39:55.993 --> 00:39:58.095
But it's already over in my mind.

00:39:59.363 --> 00:40:01.132
-Really?
-Yeah.

00:40:01.198 --> 00:40:03.734
-I thought you'd definitely choose Kazuto.
-I know.

00:40:04.568 --> 00:40:08.839
I wanted to reset my feelings
before expressing them again.

00:40:09.507 --> 00:40:10.741
-To who?
-You.

00:40:11.242 --> 00:40:12.410
-Me?
-Yeah.

00:40:13.444 --> 00:40:14.378
It's Dai.

00:40:14.445 --> 00:40:15.679
We were right.

00:40:15.746 --> 00:40:17.681
-It was Dai.
-It was.

00:40:18.182 --> 00:40:20.251
I've been thinking about it.

00:40:20.317 --> 00:40:21.952
-Here's a letter…
-What?

00:40:22.787 --> 00:40:23.988
…that I wrote.

00:40:25.890 --> 00:40:26.957
I thought I'd read it.

00:40:28.325 --> 00:40:29.794
-"Dear Dai."
-Yes.

00:40:29.860 --> 00:40:34.198
"I didn't think I could convey
my feelings well, so I put it in writing."

00:40:35.833 --> 00:40:37.001
"First, I want to ask,

00:40:37.568 --> 00:40:38.836
are you happy now?"

00:40:41.305 --> 00:40:43.707
"I was glad to meet
someone the same age as me."

00:40:43.774 --> 00:40:45.509
"I wanted to get to know you."

00:40:45.576 --> 00:40:47.945
"We got along,
and I thought you were fun."

00:40:48.012 --> 00:40:49.513
"The day of the go-kart contest,

00:40:49.580 --> 00:40:53.417
I had decided I'd ask Kazuto out
on a date if I won,

00:40:53.984 --> 00:40:56.287
but, in fact,
you were in the back of my mind."

00:40:57.188 --> 00:40:59.690
"Though I had feelings for you,

00:40:59.757 --> 00:41:03.027
as I learned about the relationship
between you and Shun,

00:41:03.093 --> 00:41:05.095
I found myself stepping back."

00:41:06.330 --> 00:41:08.065
"I don't mean to compare,

00:41:08.132 --> 00:41:13.304
but when thinking about the ten things
I like about my crush, as Shun suggested,

00:41:13.871 --> 00:41:16.774
I easily came up with more for you."

00:41:18.008 --> 00:41:20.411
You like Kazuto, right?

00:41:21.312 --> 00:41:22.680
What do you like about him?

00:41:22.746 --> 00:41:27.685
I hear it's a good sign
if you can come up with ten things.

00:41:30.855 --> 00:41:35.092
"When I thought about my feelings
honestly, my feelings for you grew."

00:41:35.159 --> 00:41:38.796
"Sometimes I felt a bit jealous
when you were with Shun."

00:41:40.197 --> 00:41:41.999
"I often went to you for advice."

00:41:42.800 --> 00:41:44.902
"I also heard a lot about Shun from you."

00:41:44.969 --> 00:41:49.306
"At times, I saw you treated
in a way I would've hated."

00:41:49.907 --> 00:41:51.609
"I wouldn't let you feel anxious."

00:41:52.176 --> 00:41:53.677
"I wouldn't let you feel bad."

00:41:54.311 --> 00:41:56.614
"I'd show you such loving care."

00:41:57.515 --> 00:42:01.719
"I'd put your feelings first,
and I'd make you happy right now."

00:42:03.153 --> 00:42:07.758
"Can you think of me as a romantic partner
and not just as a friend?"

00:42:17.134 --> 00:42:22.072
He conveyed his feelings honestly to me.

00:42:23.941 --> 00:42:27.011
I'm happy but confused.

00:42:44.395 --> 00:42:47.898
Are you happier being loved
or being the one to love?

00:42:47.965 --> 00:42:49.500
Yeah, this is like a TV drama!

00:42:49.567 --> 00:42:52.303
-Yeah, it is.
-This is what happens on TV dramas!

00:42:52.369 --> 00:42:54.038
And the next one is the last one!

00:42:54.104 --> 00:42:55.506
-No!
-I don't want that!

00:42:55.573 --> 00:42:57.841
-No way they could wrap it up.
-What'll happen?

00:42:57.908 --> 00:43:00.110
How could it wrap up
in just one more episode?